obeandmail.com/arts/film/film-reviews/secrets-and-lives-of-hasidic-women/article18703691/|title=The Globe & Mail|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|Editor, Writer, Camera\n|90 minute\ndocumentary\n\n''(Radio Canada)''\n|<nowiki>-Best Documentary at Crown Heights Film Festival.</nowiki><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.crownheightsfilmfestival.com/2019-festival|title=2020 Festival|website=Mysite|language=en|access-date=2019-10-20}}</ref>\n|-\n|2013\n|''Big Wind'' <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://hnmag.ca/tv/canwea-responds-to-tvo-doc-big-wind/|title=Hollywood North Magazine|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|Editor, Writer, Camera\n|90 minute\ndocumentary\n\n''(TVO)''\n|\n|-\n|2013\n|Space Race 2\n|Editor\n|76 minute\ndocumentary\n\n''(CTV)''\n|\n|-\n|2014\n|''The Wolverine: The Fight of the James Bay Cree'' <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hotdocs.ca/archive/films/wolverine-the-fight-of-the-james-bay-cree|title=Hotdocs|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|Editor, Writer\n|10 minute\ndocumentary\n|\n|-\n|2014\n|''[[Sol (film)|Sol]]'' <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tpt.org/sol/|title=PBS TV|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|Editor\n|90 minute\ndocumentary\n\n''(Super Chanel)''\n|  -Grand Prize for Best Canadian Feature at the [[Rencontres internationales du documentaire de Montr\u00e9al|RIDM Montreal International Documentary Festival]], 2014.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://nationtalk.ca/story/sol-riveting-documentary-about-youth-suicide-in-nunavut-has-world-premiere-at-imaginenative-film-festival|title=Nation Talk|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n-[[Canada's Top Ten]] feature films of 2014 by the [[Toronto International Film Festival]], (TIFF).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/ent